---
/**
 * A progressive-hint ladder for a problem: the reader reveals one `<Hint>` at a
 * time (nudge → method → solution) to self-scaffold. Pure `<details>`, no JS.
 * Hints auto-number ("Hint 1", "Hint 2", …) via a scoped counter reset here;
 * mark the final rung `<Hint solution>` for a "Løsning" closer.
 */
---

<div class="hints" role="group" aria-label="Hint"><slot /></div>

<style>
  .hints {
    counter-reset: hint;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-block: var(--space-5);
  }
</style>
